<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>404 - 语录管理</title>
    <style>
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
        body {
            background: #1a1a2e;
            color: #e0e0e0;
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, sans-serif;
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }
        .container {
            background: #16213e;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 40px;
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 400px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(0,0,0,.3);
            text-align: center;
        }
        h1 { font-size: 48px; color: #e94560; margin-bottom: 8px; }
        p { font-size: 15px; color: #888; margin-bottom: 24px; line-height: 1.6; }
        a { color: #e94560; text-decoration: none; font-size: 14px; }
        a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
        #back-button {
            position: fixed; top: 20px; left: 20px; font-size: 24px;
            text-decoration: none; background: #222; color: #eee;
            padding: 6px 12px; border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 5px rgba(0,0,0,.4); z-index: 1000;
            transition: background .2s;
        }
        #back-button:hover { background: #333; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<a href="javascript:history.back()" id="back-button" title="返回">←</a>
<div class="container">
    <h1>404</h1>
    <p>
        <%= message %><br>
        该群可能不存在语录，或尚未被添加到你的访问列表中。
    </p>
    <a href="/manage">返回管理面板</a>
</div>
</body>
</html>
